    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>踮脚立于悬崖的旅人，莽撞的愚者走进冒险！谣言勒紧咽喉，心跳之路荆棘丛生。双生灵魂囚禁同一躯体，血色与爱意共同迎接审判。编造谣言的共犯，要何去何从？</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/2f0902c93fd27505c1eff99dda2ccaef.avif?t=1749933448\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras_big/2f0902c93fd27505c1eff99dda2ccaef.avif?t=1749933448 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事简介</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >小镇流传着一则怪谈，当午夜的钟声敲响，便能在学校内找到那间「不存在的教室」，传闻中，教室有着唤回逝者灵魂的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暑假刚开始，肖文非便等不及带着青梅竹马斐小月前往学校，他计划利用怪谈制造一场特别的惊喜，从而将深埋已久的情愫告诉小月……他们成功的找到了这间教室，但之后发生的事情却远远超乎了两人的预料。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当肖文非再次醒来，女孩却已不见，文非打开笔记本内的记录，却得知小月的灵魂竟然寄宿在自己的身体里！只是，两人中只能有一个，处于苏醒状态。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了解开「诅咒」，少年和少女对神秘教室展开了全面调查。他们将在这场奇妙的冒险中，不断搜集各种线索，随着线索的积累，摆在二人面前的，是一个更加残酷的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法介绍</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索小镇获得线索。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/127a452863ff910a926a81bdce5d104e.poster.avif?t=1749933448\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/127a452863ff910a926a81bdce5d104e.webm?t=1749933448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/127a452863ff910a926a81bdce5d104e.mp4?t=1749933448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >向关键人物举证线索推动剧情。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/75fcd3902d74e7b5b57dfb03fd8e9ec9.poster.avif?t=1749933448\" width=800 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/75fcd3902d74e7b5b57dfb03fd8e9ec9.webm?t=1749933448\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/75fcd3902d74e7b5b57dfb03fd8e9ec9.mp4?t=1749933448\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>关于试用版</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >试用版只包含三个章节中，第一个章节的第一天的内容。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 试用版包含本游戏的主要玩法，以及大部分剧情的叙事风格展示。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人物介绍</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/5a2224d5bb0f2df574b758a2204737d8.avif?t=1749933448\" width=267 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>肖文非</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个中二病的学生，整天沉迷在超自然世界中，充满正义感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他带着斐小月深夜来到学校寻找一间“多出来的教室”，然而这次让他碰到真的超自然力量了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3270690/extras/4d2399103828e40656c1fb0280019813.avif?t=1749933448\" width=267 height=413 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>斐小月</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >肖文非的朋友，她生活在一个重组家庭，虽然成绩很好，但是似乎没有得到家里的重视。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >肖文非半夜带着她来到学校寻找一间“多出来的教室”，但斐小月对于此却有自己的心思。</p>",
